{"title":"小高炉颂","authors":["宋家玲","阎子祥","马占鳌","高山"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":9,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小高炉颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座高炉一朵花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"座座小高炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵钢铁花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花儿虽然小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花多香味大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的光芒照耀它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经得起风吹和雨打；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进之水勤灌溉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花儿越开越壮大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"座座小高炉，条条像瀑布。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲得人心激浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲得敌人坐不住。人心激浪花，身上劲更足；敌人坐不住，低头来认输。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（宋家玲）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水冲跑万重山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片钢铁山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片高炉排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片烟火苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片劳动海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼铁气焰高烧云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水冲跑万重山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（抚顺阎子祥）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小高炉颂一唱小高炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地星罗布；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日建千万座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古今中外无。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二唱小高炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长的真威武；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一口吞三山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腹内盛五湖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三唱小高炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾似瀑布；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金河天上落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁水日夜出。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四唱小高炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人落了伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月也服输。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（沈阳重型机器厂马占鳌）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小高炉生得俏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小高炉，生得俏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼻孔朝天咧嘴笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑得高山都献宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑得铁水翻花跳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（包头红旗人民公社高山）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}